{"tid":874214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共幹部蔡奇晤林鄭月娥  指港珠澳橋為新世界奇蹟","createTime":"2018-10-24T04:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T08:17:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c255ede1c6b06bfff1e6fadf8fce39640ada168e","tid":874214,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"正在訪京的行政長官林鄭月娥，與北京市委書記蔡奇會面。蔡奇表示，港珠澳大橋是連接三地新的世界奇蹟，能進一步體現一國兩制強大生命力。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥向北京市長陳吉寧表示，香港有一國和兩制的雙重優勢，相信京港雙方會繼續以積極務實的態度，深化合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B8%82%E5%A7%94%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%E8%94%A1%E5%A5%87%E6%99%A4%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E6%A9%8B%E7%82%BA%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F-041013974.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A5%2587%25E6%2599%25A4%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25A9%258B%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%25B9%259F-041013974.html&d=PLqY17On9GjrtTpqPr5A8f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=78a9dad4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B8%82%E5%A7%94%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%E8%94%A1%E5%A5%87%E6%99%A4%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E6%A9%8B%E7%82%BA%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F-041013974.html</a>"},{"pid":"f980c718609377927cfcfcda1c2fefce463b58b8","tid":874214,"uid":90,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"最高造價嘅垃圾？（人工島未起唔計）"},{"pid":"7b3ea045f513f0de3c988917af59a839372a054f","tid":874214,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"呢件蔡京<br />\n被人叫 蔡包子 <br />\n<br />\n佢老細 慶豐包子帝 親嫡系<img src=\"/